    metaTitle: "Botox for Men in Media & On Camera — TV, YouTube, Podcast Guide",
    description: "If your face appears on camera regularly — TV, YouTube, podcasts, film — Botox works differently for you than it does for a civilian. The lights, the angles, and the high-def scrutiny change everything. Here's what on-camera men need to know.",
